      <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
        <h6 class="text-white fw-bold mb-3 text-uppercase small">Connect With Us</h6>
        <p class="text-light mb-3" style="font-size: 0.9rem;">
          Join our community of music enthusiasts and collectors.
        </p>
        
        <div class="d-flex gap-3 mb-4">
          <a href="#" class="text-white text-decoration-none social-icon" aria-label="Instagram">
            <i class="bi bi-instagram" style="font-size: 1.25rem;"></i>
